  "title": "fix(QueryRuleCustomData): pass data as object to templates",
  "body": "The `QueryRuleCustomData` component passed the `items` as an array to users' templates. This made them unusable with Hogan. By passing `items` within an object, they're now accessible.\r\n\r\nI added a story to demo how to use Hogan with these widgets.",
